Package: jsfR
Title: R Interface to the Jump-Switch-Flow Stochastic Simulator
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Vaibhav", "Manihar", email = "vaibhav.manihar@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an R wrapper around the Python 'jsf' package for
    hybrid stochastic-deterministic simulation of compartmental models. The
    Jump-Switch-Flow (JSF) algorithm dynamically switches compartments
    between discrete (Continuous Time Markov Chain) and continuous (ODE)
    representations based on population-size thresholds. This package uses
    'reticulate' to call the Python implementation from R.
